description:
This is an image captured by me,  processed by my friend, Mr. Eric Coles, in the positive B / W version but taken over and processed by me in the inverted version, starting from the point where Eric arrived here: 
https: //www.astrobin .com / sre5mc / B /? image_list_page = 3 & nc = & nce =

The line that Eric started seems very interesting, which allowed me to get an interesting  inverted version (as fun). I would say, just as interesting, using, among other things, HDR technology. Thanks, Eric, for your initial interesting processing line and I hope, you didn't mind me. Of course, the image still requires me to work on it, for a perfect finish.
title: "Radiography" for AR12665 and AR12666 of July 7, 2017. Inverted version.
